examples.en: The clock in the hall chimed six.
The music and the mood chimed well together.
The blue dress chimes in with the colour of her eyes.
examples.ru: Это синее платье в тон её глазам.

examples.en: Her views on life didn't quite chime with mine.
examples.ru: Ее взгляды на жизнь не вполне созвучны с моими.
